 the country, Sam and Erwan talk with local surfers Dihya and Walid about the future of surfing in Algeria and how the emergence of the sport could impact the people there." type="episode" contentRating="NR" duration="1800000" grandparentArt="https://images.frequency.com/video/7381010443655473386/solid/rectangle/w1920_h1080/1a57p19h14pzx14ptewfmorw31.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/690161068c0415b0db4efc5f" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/690161068c0415b0db4efc5f" grandparentRatingKey="690161068c0415b0db4efc5f" grandparentThumb="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/8a626fbd-6e1b-48ad-b36a-c634423b9677/2000X3000_WSL_VERT.jpg" grandparentTitle="Brilliant Corners" grandparentType="show" index="3" originallyAvailableAt="2025-10-06T17:00:18Z" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://images.frequency.com/video/7381010430892568360/solid/rectangle/w1920_h1080/18sff3i0h8n1v17tnn2g02nr9j.jpg" title="Trans-Saharan Highway | Brilliant Corners: Algeria, Episode 3" userState="0" year="2025"><Image alt="Trans-Saharan Highway | Brilliant Corners: Algeria, Episode 3" type="coverArt" url="https://images.frequency.com/video/7381010443655473386/solid/rectangle/w1920_h1080/1a57p19h14pzx14ptewfmorw31.jpg"/><Image alt="Trans-Saharan Highway | Brilliant Corners: Algeria, Episode 3" type="coverPoster" url="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/8a626fbd-6e1b-48ad-b36a-c634423b9677/2000X3000_WSL_VERT.jpg"/><Image alt="Trans-Saharan Highway | Brilliant Corners: Algeria, Episode 3" type="snapshot" url="https://images.frequency.com/video/7381010430892568360/solid/rectangle/w1920_h1080/18sff3i0h8n1v17tnn2g02nr9j.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" id="620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" ratingKey="genre_620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" slug="sports" tag="Sports" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1774506600" duration="1800000" endsAt="1774508400" id="69b2b2ba